[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/SYSTEM_FILE_STRUCTURE_GUIDE.tt,v 1.0 2025/09/27 11:06 Shanta Exp shanta ' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<h1 id="file_structure_top"><a href="#file_structure_top">System Documentation File Structure Guide</a></h1>

<h3>Quick Navigation</h3>
<p>
    <a href="#overview">Overview</a> | 
    <a href="#directory_structure">Directory Structure</a> | 
    <a href="#file_templates">File Templates</a> | 
    <a href="#naming_conventions">Naming Conventions</a> | 
    <a href="#include_patterns">Include Patterns</a> | 
    <a href="#checklist">Implementation Checklist</a>
</p>

<div class="container info" id="overview">
    <div class="container-header">Documentation Structure Overview</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <p>This guide defines the comprehensive file structure required for complete system documentation following the ENCY.md success pattern. Each system should have a main overview document that includes sub-documents for specific components.</p>
            
            <div class="principle-grid">
                <div class="principle-card">
                    <h4>Main System Document</h4>
                    <p>Single comprehensive overview with includes for all components</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle-card">
                    <h4>Modular Sub-Documents</h4>
                    <p>Separate .tt files for each component, included via containers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle-card">
                    <h4>Role-Based Documentation</h4>
                    <p>Specific docs for admin, user, and developer audiences</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle-card">
                    <h4>Unique Navigation</h4>
                    <p>Each document has navigation unique to its content and scope</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container primary" id="directory_structure">
    <div class="container-header">Required Directory Structure</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>Complete Documentation File Tree</h3>
            
            <div class="directory-tree">
                <div class="tree-section">
                    <h4>📁 Documentation/</h4>
                    <div class="tree-content">
                        <div class="tree-item main">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME].md <span class="description">Main system overview document</span></div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 controllers/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Controller.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]AdminController.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]APIController.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]AuthController.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 models/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Model.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]DataModel.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]ValidationModel.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]SearchModel.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 utils/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]DataUtils.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]ValidationUtils.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]SearchUtils.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]ExportUtils.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 scripts/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME].pm.md <span class="note">Documents the main .pm file</span></div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.pm.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Setup.pl.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Migration.pl.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 templates/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Index.tt.md <span class="note">Documents the .tt template</span></div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Form.tt.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Display.tt.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Admin.tt.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]Report.tt.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 config/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_config.json.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_database.conf.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_routes.conf.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 guidelines/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_guidelines.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_coding_standards.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_data_standards.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_security_guidelines.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 admin/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_installation.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_configuration.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_maintenance.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_troubleshooting.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_backup.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_security.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_monitoring.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 roles/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-content">
                                <div class="tree-sub-branch">
                                    <h6>📁 normal/ <span class="note">End user documentation</span></h6>
                                    <div class="tree-items">
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_getting_started.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_ui_guide.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_faq.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_best_practices.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_shortcuts.md</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="tree-sub-branch">
                                    <h6>📁 admin/ <span class="note">Administrator-specific docs</span></h6>
                                    <div class="tree-items">
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_admin_guide.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_user_management.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_system_monitoring.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_data_management.md</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="tree-sub-branch">
                                    <h6>📁 developer/ <span class="note">Developer documentation</span></h6>
                                    <div class="tree-items">
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_development_setup.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_architecture.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_api.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_testing.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_extensions.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_deployment.md</div>
                                        <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_database_schema.md</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tree-branch">
                            <h5>📁 tutorials/</h5>
                            <div class="tree-items">
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_tutorials.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_basic_tutorial.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_advanced_tutorial.md</div>
                                <div class="tree-item">📄 [SYSTEM_NAME]_integration_tutorial.md</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container secondary" id="file_templates">
    <div class="container-header">Standard File Templates</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>Template Structure for Different File Types</h3>
            
            <div class="template-section">
                <h4>Controller Documentation Template</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]Controller.tt,v 1.0 YYYY/MM/DD Author Exp author ' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

&lt;h2 id="controller_overview"&gt;[SYSTEM_NAME] Controller Overview&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class="controller-nav"&gt;
    &lt;a href="#methods"&gt;Methods&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#routes"&gt;Routes&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#dependencies"&gt;Dependencies&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="controller-content"&gt;
    &lt;h3 id="methods"&gt;Controller Methods&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]_methods.tt' %]
    
    &lt;h3 id="routes"&gt;Route Mappings&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]_routes.tt' %]
    
    &lt;h3 id="dependencies"&gt;Dependencies&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]_dependencies.tt' %]
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="template-section">
                <h4>Model Documentation Template</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]Model.tt,v 1.0 YYYY/MM/DD Author Exp author ' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

&lt;h2 id="model_overview"&gt;[SYSTEM_NAME] Model Overview&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class="model-nav"&gt;
    &lt;a href="#attributes"&gt;Attributes&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#relationships"&gt;Relationships&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#methods"&gt;Methods&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#validation"&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="model-content"&gt;
    &lt;h3 id="attributes"&gt;Model Attributes&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]_attributes.tt' %]
    
    &lt;h3 id="relationships"&gt;Database Relationships&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]_relationships.tt' %]
    
    &lt;h3 id="methods"&gt;Model Methods&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]_methods.tt' %]
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="template-section">
                <h4>Utility Documentation Template</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/utils/[SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.tt,v 1.0 YYYY/MM/DD Author Exp author ' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

&lt;h2 id="utils_overview"&gt;[SYSTEM_NAME] Utilities Overview&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class="utils-nav"&gt;
    &lt;a href="#functions"&gt;Functions&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#constants"&gt;Constants&lt;/a&gt; | 
    &lt;a href="#examples"&gt;Usage Examples&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="utils-content"&gt;
    &lt;h3 id="functions"&gt;Utility Functions&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/utils/[SYSTEM_NAME]_functions.tt' %]
    
    &lt;h3 id="constants"&gt;Constants and Configuration&lt;/h3&gt;
    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/utils/[SYSTEM_NAME]_constants.tt' %]
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container info" id="naming_conventions">
    <div class="container-header">Naming Conventions</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>File Naming Standards</h3>
            
            <div class="naming-grid">
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Main System Document</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME].md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCY.md, BACKUP.md, USER.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Controller Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME]Controller.md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCYController.md, BackupController.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Model Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME]Model.md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCYModel.md, UserModel.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Utility Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCYUtils.md, ValidationUtils.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Script Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SCRIPT_NAME].pm.md</div>
                    <p>Examples: DataProcessor.pm.md, EmailSender.pm.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Template Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[TEMPLATE_NAME].tt.md</div>
                    <p>Examples: IndexPage.tt.md, ReportForm.tt.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Admin Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME]_[PURPOSE].md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCY_installation.md, backup_configuration.md</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="naming-card">
                    <h4>Role-Based Documentation</h4>
                    <div class="naming-example">[SYSTEM_NAME]_[DOCUMENT_TYPE].md</div>
                    <p>Examples: ENCY_user_guide.md, backup_api.md</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="naming-rules">
                <h3>Naming Rules</h3>
                <div class="rule-list">
                    <div class="rule-item">
                        <strong>System Names:</strong> Use ALL CAPS for system abbreviations (ENCY, USER, BACKUP)
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-item">
                        <strong>File Extensions:</strong> Always use .md for working documentation files
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-item">
                        <strong>Underscores:</strong> Use underscores to separate words in compound names
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-item">
                        <strong>Descriptive Names:</strong> Include the purpose/type in the filename
                    </div>
                    <div class="rule-item">
                        <strong>Consistent Patterns:</strong> Follow the same pattern across all systems
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container primary" id="include_patterns">
    <div class="container-header">Include Patterns & Container Structure</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>Standard Include Patterns</h3>
            
            <div class="pattern-section">
                <h4>Basic Container with Include</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>&lt;div class="container primary"&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-header" id="section_id"&gt;Section Title&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container-content-inner"&gt;
            [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/to/file.tt' %]
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pattern-section">
                <h4>Multi-Component Section</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>&lt;div class="container secondary"&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-header" id="multi_section"&gt;Multi-Component Section&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container-content-inner"&gt;
            &lt;h3&gt;Component 1&lt;/h3&gt;
            [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/component1.tt' %]
            
            &lt;h3&gt;Component 2&lt;/h3&gt;
            [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/component2.tt' %]
            
            &lt;h3&gt;Component 3&lt;/h3&gt;
            [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/component3.tt' %]
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pattern-section">
                <h4>Warning/Alert Container</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>&lt;div class="container warning"&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-header" id="warning_section"&gt;Important Information&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container-content-inner"&gt;
            &lt;div class="alert alert-warning"&gt;
                &lt;h3&gt;⚠️ CRITICAL: Important Notice&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Important information here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/warning_content.tt' %]
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pattern-section">
                <h4>Grid Layout with Includes</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code>&lt;div class="container info"&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-header" id="grid_section"&gt;Grid Section&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="container-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container-content-inner"&gt;
            &lt;div class="grid-layout"&gt;
                &lt;div class="grid-item"&gt;
                    &lt;h4&gt;Grid Item 1&lt;/h4&gt;
                    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/item1.tt' %]
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div class="grid-item"&gt;
                    &lt;h4&gt;Grid Item 2&lt;/h4&gt;
                    [% INCLUDE 'Documentation/path/item2.tt' %]
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="container-types">
                <h3>Container Types</h3>
                <div class="type-grid">
                    <div class="type-card">
                        <h4>container primary</h4>
                        <p>Main content sections (controllers, models, core features)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="type-card">
                        <h4>container secondary</h4>
                        <p>Supporting content (utilities, files, configurations)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="type-card">
                        <h4>container info</h4>
                        <p>Informational content (overviews, explanations)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="type-card">
                        <h4>container warning</h4>
                        <p>Important notices, migration notes, critical information</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="type-card">
                        <h4>container success</h4>
                        <p>Positive information, completed features, success guides</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container success" id="checklist">
    <div class="container-header">Implementation Checklist</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>System Documentation Implementation Checklist</h3>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 1: Main Document Setup</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create main [SYSTEM_NAME].md file using template</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Replace all [PLACEHOLDER] values with system-specific information</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Update Quick Navigation with system-specific sections</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Update PageVersion with correct file path and version</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Customize system overview and description</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 2: Core Component Documentation</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]Controller.md</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]Model.md</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create Documentation/utils/[SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.md</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document all .pm files in Documentation/scripts/</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document all .tt files in Documentation/templates/</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 3: Role-Based Documentation</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create admin documentation in Documentation/admin/</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create user documentation in Documentation/roles/normal/</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create developer documentation in Documentation/roles/developer/</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create guidelines in Documentation/guidelines/</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create tutorials in Documentation/tutorials/</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 4: Database & API Documentation</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document complete database structure</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document all API endpoints</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create database migration documentation</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document configuration files</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create backup and recovery procedures</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 5: Implementation Planning</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create detailed implementation plan</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document technical requirements</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create migration strategy if applicable</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Document testing procedures</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Create deployment documentation</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="checklist-section">
                <h4>Phase 6: Quality Assurance</h4>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Verify all includes point to existing files</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Test all navigation links</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Ensure consistent formatting across all documents</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Review for completeness and accuracy</div>
                    <div class="checklist-item">□ Update version numbers in all PageVersion headers</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container primary">
    <div class="container-header">Example File Creation Sequence</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>Recommended File Creation Order</h3>
            
            <div class="sequence-step">
                <h4>Step 1: Main Document</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code># Create main system document
cp SYSTEM_DOCUMENTATION_TEMPLATE.md [SYSTEM_NAME].md
# Edit [SYSTEM_NAME].md and replace all placeholders</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sequence-step">
                <h4>Step 2: Core Components</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code># Create controller documentation
touch Documentation/controllers/[SYSTEM_NAME]Controller.md

# Create model documentation  
touch Documentation/models/[SYSTEM_NAME]Model.md

# Create utilities documentation
touch Documentation/utils/[SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.md</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sequence-step">
                <h4>Step 3: File Documentation</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code># Document Perl modules
touch Documentation/scripts/[SYSTEM_NAME].pm.md
touch Documentation/scripts/[SYSTEM_NAME]Utils.pm.md

# Document templates
touch Documentation/templates/[SYSTEM_NAME]Index.tt.md
touch Documentation/templates/[SYSTEM_NAME]Form.tt.md</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sequence-step">
                <h4>Step 4: Role-Based Docs</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code># Admin documentation
mkdir -p Documentation/admin
touch Documentation/admin/[SYSTEM_NAME]_installation.md
touch Documentation/admin/[SYSTEM_NAME]_configuration.md

# User documentation
mkdir -p Documentation/roles/normal
touch Documentation/roles/normal/[SYSTEM_NAME]_user_guide.md

# Developer documentation
mkdir -p Documentation/roles/developer
touch Documentation/roles/developer/[SYSTEM_NAME]_api.md</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sequence-step">
                <h4>Step 5: Supporting Documents</h4>
                <div class="code-block">
                    <pre><code># Guidelines and tutorials
mkdir -p Documentation/guidelines
touch Documentation/guidelines/[SYSTEM_NAME]_guidelines.md

mkdir -p Documentation/tutorials
touch Documentation/tutorials/[SYSTEM_NAME]_tutorials.md</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="back-to-top">
    <p id="return_top"><a href="#file_structure_top">Return to Top</a></p>
</div>